high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the counter.
Put the large metal knife handle up in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the large metal knife in it off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Put the mug with the large metal knife in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a large metal knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, turn right to enter the kitchen, and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Place the knife in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around, walk to the sink, and turn right to face it.
Place the cup in the front middle section of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the chair, then turn right and walk to the large knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right towards the mug on the counter top.
Put the knife in the mug.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink, in front of the plastic container.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it inside a sink basin.
